room_title: Escape room "Excalibur" by Labyrinth Escape Games in Portland
room_description: Long ago, King Arthur ruled his land with benevolence and wisdom. He banished darkness from his kingdom with the help of his knights and his sword Excalibur. When his reign was coming to an end he knew that evil would eventually return. When that time came a new ruler would be needed to protect his kingdom. He devised a series of tests for subjects to test their wits and resolve, and prove their worth to wield EXCALIBUR!
